      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and I\u2019ve kept up with every single service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
